<0xC3><0x81>lvarez explained that "Super Mario 3D Land" was "the first Nintendo video game to be developed for this console from the very beginning", because until now, success articles such as "Star Fox 64 3D" or "Zelda: Ocarine of time 3D" were adaptations of already existing titles.
